    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure peak variable valve timing performance. The drivetrain features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Suspension has been refreshed with Bilstein dampers for improved turn-in and lateral stability. While the aesthetics show light road patina consistent with enthusiast use, the powertrain and chassis dynamics remain sharp and responsive.",
