      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and represents a fantastic balance of luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster, though a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel reflect its honest history on the road. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver's bolster, and the wood trim is free of cracks. Every electronic feature\u2014from the heated seats and navigation to the premium surround-sound system\u2014is fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been treated to synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the most recent service included a fresh set of brake pads and a comprehensive fluid flush. The engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. This car has been garage-kept, smoke-free, and comes with a complete folder of service records. It is a turn-key example ready for its next long-term owner.",
